@teatrunk is back with its favorite art activity - Painting with Tea, led by artist and arts facilitator @arubose

While we love drinking garam chai on cool days, and enjoy iced teas on hot days - have you ever tried painting with our teas?
If not, this is THE experience for you!
And if you have, then bring a friend along, and enjoy a Sunday evening together!

Join us for a 'Painting with Tea' art workshop, at the cosy Tea Trunk Tea Room, Fontainhas.

Date: 23 April 2023, Sunday
Venue: Tea Trunk Tea Room
Ticket: INR 1399/-
(Includes all art-making materials, a refreshing beverage and a delicious dessert)

This workshop is open to adults and kids (8 years and up). So parents, bring your kids along! Kiddos, tell your parents to take you for a fun evening at the Tea Trunk Tea Room!

📌What does a tea sommelier do differently when making an iced matcha latte?🤫
We’re spilling the secrets in this step-by-step guide to help you nail it at home.🍵🫶🏽
✨Pro tip: Add a pinch of sea salt to balance the earthiness and make the matcha pop!
.
.
#tea #matcha #matchalatte #matchalover #teasommelier

Recipe ➡️
Try this simple recipe to elevate your tea time:
✨Brew a cup of delicate rose oolong tea and let it cool.
✨In a jar or shaker, combine the tea, fresh lemon juice, honey, and ice.
✨Shake well for a  blend of flavors.
✨Pour over ice, adding a touch of citrus freshness.
✨Garnish with a lemon wedge and delicate rose petals for a subtle floral note.
Sip, savor, and enjoy the refined simplicity. 🌹
